title: Supporting Yourself
itunes:title: Supporting Yourself
description:
Supporting yourself, whether you're single or have a big family, is always the same. You have to develop your own inner support system.
 
The most devastating thought you can have is that you don't have anyone to help you lose weight.
 
This podcast will change all that. I'll teach you how to develop your own support system and why it's so important to start with supporting yourself.
 
Get the Free Course here:
http://phit.click/freecourse
